Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.14,0:00:02.14,SU,,0,0,0,,\N- # We # - # Are the Crystal #
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.14,0:00:05.79,SU,,0,0,0,,\N- # Gems # - # we'll always save the day #
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.85,0:00:07.92,SU,,0,0,0,,\N♪ and if you think we can't ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.93,0:00:10.79,SU,,0,0,0,,\N♪ we'll always find a way ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.79,0:00:14.70,SU,,0,0,0,,\N- # that's why the people # - # of this world #
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.70,0:00:17.07,SU,,0,0,0,,\N♪ believe in... Garnet ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.07,0:00:19.87,SU,,0,0,0,,\N- # Amethyst # - # and Pearl #
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.87,0:00:21.54,SU,,0,0,0,,\N♪ And Steven! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.98,0:00:26.98,SU,,0,0,0,,再次谢谢你们在我离开的时候\NThanks again for protecting Beach City
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.02,0:00:28.38,SU,,0,0,0,,保护了海滩市,康妮\Nwhile I was gone, Connie.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.42,0:00:30.95,SU,,0,0,0,,没关系,既然你已经从太空回来了\NNo problem. And now that you're back from space,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.99,0:00:34.12,SU,,0,0,0,,那我就正式转让我对你的床的控制权\NI officially relinquish control of your bed to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.16,0:00:36.89,SU,,0,0,0,,谢谢你帮我暖被窝,长官\NThank you for keeping it warm, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.03,0:00:41.59,SU,,0,0,0,,我也希望你爹能喜欢新的洗车店招牌\NI hope your dad liked the new car wash sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.60,0:00:42.56,SU,,0,0,0,,他喜欢死了\NHe loved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.60,0:00:43.76,SU,,0,0,0,,相信招牌挂起来之后\NI'm sure it'll look great
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.80,0:00:45.36,SU,,0,0,0,,一定会很好看的\Nwhen the Gems are done putting it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.37,0:00:47.90,SU,,0,0,0,,我希望宝石们能在我走之前回来,好告个别\NI hope they're back in time for me to say bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.94,0:00:50.30,SU,,0,0,0,,呃...可能要等好一会儿了\NUh... It might be a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.34,0:00:52.22,SU,,0,0,0,,你根本想不到让她们一起做事\NYou wouldn't believe how many of them it takes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.23,0:00:53.17,SU,,0,0,0,,是有多困难呢\Nto screw in a light bulb.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.21,0:00:55.94,SU,,0,0,0,,我在想我妈到哪儿了\NI wonder where my mom is.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.98,0:00:59.48,SU,,0,0,0,,她早该来接我了\NShe should have been here to pick me up by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.75,0:01:02.71,SU,,0,0,0,,这里是麦雪仑医生\NYou've reached Dr. Maheswaran.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.72,0:01:05.48,SU,,0,0,0,,请留言,如果你是我的病人的话\NPlease leave a message, and if you're one of my patients,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.49,0:01:07.05,SU,,0,0,0,,你不该有这个号码的!\Nyou shouldn't have this number!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.09,0:01:08.62,SU,,0,0,0,,她不接电话\NShe's not answering.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.66,0:01:11.36,SU,,0,0,0,,这个,想想好的一面!\NWell, look on the bright side!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.40,0:01:13.46,SU,,0,0,0,,现在咱俩能多玩一会儿了\NNow we can hang out a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.50,0:01:14.99,SU,,0,0,0,,我相信她肯定会来的\NI'm sure she'll show up eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.00,0:01:16.46,SU,,0,0,0,,我不是特别想缠着你\NI don't want to impose.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.50,0:01:18.66,SU,,0,0,0,,我意思是,你脑袋里肯定很乱\NI mean, you must have a lot to think about
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.67,0:01:20.20,SU,,0,0,0,,毕竟刚经过了太空冒险\Nafter your space adventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.27,0:01:21.63,SU,,0,0,0,,你还差点弄丢了你爹\NYou almost lost your dad,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.64,0:01:25.27,SU,,0,0,0,,还有这些关于钻石们和你妈妈的事...\Nand all that stuff about the diamonds and your mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.31,0:01:27.64,SU,,0,0,0,,如果你想要点私人空间的话我也能理解\NI'd understand if you need some space.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.68,0:01:32.01,SU,,0,0,0,,才不,现在我最怕的就是"空间"了\NNah, the last thing I need right now is more space.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.05,0:01:33.14,SU,,0,0,0,,好吧\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.15,0:01:35.95,SU,,0,0,0,,所以现在你想玩什么?\NSo what do you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.99,0:01:37.98,SU,,0,0,0,,最后这词是个名词\NThe last word is a noun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.02,0:01:40.55,SU,,0,0,0,,呃,多层游轮\NUm, multi-hulled watercraft.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.59,0:01:42.55,SU,,0,0,0,,好,句子完成了\NOkay, here it goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.56,0:01:47.53,SU,,0,0,0,,"摇摆的糕点师烤出了古怪的糕点\N"The wiggly baker baked some new wacky pastries.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.57,0:01:49.79,SU,,0,0,0,,有蜗牛泡芙\NThere were snail puffs,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.80,0:01:53.80,SU,,0,0,0,,割草机派,还有熵玛芬"\Nlawnmower pies, and entropy muffins."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.84,0:01:55.73,SU,,0,0,0,,"大家都毛茸茸的\N"Everyone was so fuzzy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.74,0:01:57.97,SU,,0,0,0,,他们把所有东西都吃了,包括一个\Nthat they ate everything ... even the cheesecake
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.01,0:02:01.14,SU,,0,0,0,,多层游轮形状的芝士蛋糕"\Nshaped like a multi-hulled watercraft."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.38,0:02:03.88,SU,,0,0,0,,太奇怪了\NThis is really weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.92,0:02:06.78,SU,,0,0,0,,我妈从来没有不接电话过\NMy mom always answers her phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.82,0:02:07.88,SU,,0,0,0,,嗯\NHmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.92,0:02:10.48,SU,,0,0,0,,哦 我用狮子载你回家如何?\NOh. How about I give you a ride home on Lion?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.52,0:02:12.75,SU,,0,0,0,,我不是特别担心回不回家\NIt's not getting home I'm worried about.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.79,0:02:14.89,SU,,0,0,0,,要是我们在路上相互错过了怎么办?\NWhat if she shows up here and we're gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.93,0:02:17.89,SU,,0,0,0,,我们应该待在这里等她来\NWe should probably stay put until she comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.93,0:02:20.56,SU,,0,0,0,,好吧 ,反正也是等着\NWell, while we're still waiting,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.60,0:02:23.23,SU,,0,0,0,,再来一局怪句子游戏吧?\Nhow about another weird word game?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.27,0:02:24.73,SU,,0,0,0,,好吧\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.77,0:02:27.10,SU,,0,0,0,,好,我们现在需要\NAll right, let's see what we got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.14,0:02:29.10,SU,,0,0,0,,第一个词是个形容词\NFirst one is an adjective.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.14,0:02:30.87,SU,,0,0,0,,"意外的"\NAccidental.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.91,0:02:32.24,SU,,0,0,0,,"意外的"\NAccidental.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.28,0:02:33.84,SU,,0,0,0,,下一个是个名词\NAnd the next one's a noun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.88,0:02:35.07,SU,,0,0,0,,"事故"\NMishap.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.08,0:02:36.34,SU,,0,0,0,,"事故"\NMishap.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.38,0:02:37.84,SU,,0,0,0,,状语?\NAdverb?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.88,0:02:40.18,SU,,0,0,0,,"未预料地"\NUnexpectedly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.22,0:02:42.15,SU,,0,0,0,,过去时态动词?\NPast tense verb?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.19,0:02:43.65,SU,,0,0,0,,"撞毁"\NCrashed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.69,0:02:45.15,SU,,0,0,0,,名词?\NNoun?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.19,0:02:46.45,SU,,0,0,0,,"爆炸"\NExplosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.49,0:02:49.65,SU,,0,0,0,,哇哦,你真的很担心你妈妈啊,是吧?\NWow, you're really worried about your mom, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.66,0:02:53.56,SU,,0,0,0,,是啊,她从来都没有迟到过\NYeah. It's just she's never late for anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.80,0:02:58.20,SU,,0,0,0,,有人吗?\NHello?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.24,0:02:59.73,SU,,0,0,0,,我进来了\NI'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.77,0:03:00.77,SU,,0,0,0,,康妮!\NConnie!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.81,0:03:03.43,SU,,0,0,0,,妈妈!\NMom!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.44,0:03:05.04,SU,,0,0,0,,妈妈,出什么事了?\NMom, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.08,0:03:07.54,SU,,0,0,0,,我一直给你打电话,你就是不接\NI kept calling, but you weren't answering.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.58,0:03:09.74,SU,,0,0,0,,我都快吓坏了\NI was starting to freak out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.78,0:03:11.71,SU,,0,0,0,,这个手术时间太长了\NWell, surgery went long,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.75,0:03:14.05,SU,,0,0,0,,然后我又得替斯汤堡医生加班\Nand then I had to cover for Dr. Stromberg, again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.09,0:03:16.95,SU,,0,0,0,,我手机也没电了,我怀疑我的一个病人\NMy phone died, and I suspect one of my patients
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.99,0:03:18.78,SU,,0,0,0,,偷了我的充电器...\Nstole my charger and...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.59,0:03:21.55,SU,,0,0,0,,真的太对不起了,康妮\NI'm so sorry, Connie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.59,0:03:23.09,SU,,0,0,0,,没关系,妈妈\NIt's okay, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.13,0:03:25.39,SU,,0,0,0,,现在一切都好了\NEverything's fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.43,0:03:27.99,SU,,0,0,0,,谢谢你接待康妮到这么晚\NThank you for letting Connie stay late.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.03,0:03:29.09,SU,,0,0,0,,晚安,史蒂文!\NNight, Steven!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.10,0:03:30.33,SU,,0,0,0,,晚安,康妮\NNight, Connie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.37,0:03:32.53,SU,,0,0,0,,所以他刚蒸桑拿回来?\NSo he's back from the spa, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.57,0:03:35.03,SU,,0,0,0,,他刚从太空回来啦\NNo. I said space.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.04,0:03:36.90,SU,,0,0,0,,哈\NHuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.19,0:04:30.32,SU,,0,0,0,,啊,这才叫爽\NAw, that's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.08,0:04:52.74,SU,,0,0,0,,你造,有时候我会在想在墙上微笑的\NYou know, sometimes I wonder if it's even you up there...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.75,0:04:55.18,SU,,0,0,0,,是不是真正的你\Nsmiling all day and night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.22,0:04:56.95,SU,,0,0,0,,我就是想了解真正的你\NI just want to know the real you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.99,0:04:59.68,SU,,0,0,0,,而不是从别人的话语中了解你\NNot the you that everyone tells me about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.69,0:05:02.39,SU,,0,0,0,,我就是想知道事情的真相\NI just want to know the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.20,0:05:16.50,SU,,0,0,0,,呃,你好啊,房间\NUh... Hey, room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.54,0:05:18.17,SU,,0,0,0,,好久不见了,是吧?\NIt's been a bit, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:19.70,SU,,0,0,0,,那片云是你新做的?\NIs that a new cloud?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.65,0:05:23.07,SU,,0,0,0,,呃...\NUh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.08,0:05:24.28,SU,,0,0,0,,这个...\NSo...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.32,0:05:27.08,SU,,0,0,0,,我想你一定在好奇我为什么来这儿\NI suppose you're wondering why I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.12,0:05:29.81,SU,,0,0,0,,我知道这里的东西都不是真的,但是...\NI know nothing in here is real, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.82,0:05:32.22,SU,,0,0,0,,我想见见我妈妈\Nbut I want to see my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.56,0:05:45.23,SU,,0,0,0,,你好,史蒂文\NHello, Steven.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.27,0:05:47.10,SU,,0,0,0,,呃,这个...\NUm, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.14,0:05:49.00,SU,,0,0,0,,见到你很高兴\NIt's nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.94,0:05:52.37,SU,,0,0,0,,我也很高兴见到你\NIt's nice to meet you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.41,0:05:54.94,SU,,0,0,0,,呃,不好意思\NUm, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:05:57.01,SU,,0,0,0,,对我来说感觉有点奇怪\NThis is a little weird for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.05,0:05:58.34,SU,,0,0,0,,没关系的\NThat's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.38,0:06:00.28,SU,,0,0,0,,所以你现在想干嘛?\NSo what do you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.32,0:06:01.78,SU,,0,0,0,,哦,呃...\NOh, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.82,0:06:03.92,SU,,0,0,0,,我还没想过这么远\NI guess I hadn't thought that far ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.96,0:06:07.92,SU,,0,0,0,,你喜欢电子游戏吗?\NDo you like video games?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.56,0:06:12.92,SU,,0,0,0,,给我讲讲游戏规则吧,史蒂文\NSo, tell me about this game, Steven.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.93,0:06:15.59,SU,,0,0,0,,这个,这是个扳手腕游戏\NWell, I guess it's an arm-wrestling simulator,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.60,0:06:17.26,SU,,0,0,0,,是个山寨版的格斗游戏\Nwhich is spin-off of a fighting game,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.30,0:06:20.50,SU,,0,0,0,,那个格斗游戏又是个武侠剧的同人游戏\Nbased on a show about a lonely swordsman that I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.54,0:06:22.33,SU,,0,0,0,,这样解释起来就很困难了\NIt's kind of weird and hard to explain,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.34,0:06:23.67,SU,,0,0,0,,但是我喜欢\Nbut that's why I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.71,0:06:26.20,SU,,0,0,0,,听起来真的不能再好\NThat sounds just marvelous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.95,0:06:29.44,SU,,0,0,0,,K-O!\NK-O!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.48,0:06:30.98,SU,,0,0,0,,棒,我赢了!\NYeah, I won!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.02,0:06:33.21,SU,,0,0,0,,棒,你赢了!\NYay, you won.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.25,0:06:36.88,SU,,0,0,0,,还有什么亲子互动的活动来着?\NWhat else do kids do with their parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.46,0:06:46.52,SU,,0,0,0,,接得好,儿子\NNice catch, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.53,0:06:47.73,SU,,0,0,0,,真有趣\NThis is fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.77,0:06:49.76,SU,,0,0,0,,也许打棒球会更好?\NOr would baseball be better?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:53.50,SU,,0,0,0,,史蒂文,所有的体育运动都很美妙\NSteven, all sports are beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.54,0:06:56.83,SU,,0,0,0,,每个运动都是独特的体验\NEach sport is a unique experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.84,0:07:01.94,SU,,0,0,0,,肾上腺素的激发,对荣耀的追寻,力和美的展现\NThe adrenaline, the glory, the sheer feats of athleticism.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.98,0:07:07.48,SU,,0,0,0,,每个运动都是那么复杂,但又有着全同的原则\NEach one so complicated and yet exactly the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.52,0:07:09.08,SU,,0,0,0,,哇\NWhoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.12,0:07:11.95,SU,,0,0,0,,嘿,史蒂文!\NHey, Steven!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.99,0:07:14.82,SU,,0,0,0,,你造,我总感觉我的青春期\NYou know, I've always felt like something was unusual
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.86,0:07:16.29,SU,,0,0,0,,有缺少点什么东西\Nabout my adolescence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.33,0:07:19.82,SU,,0,0,0,,也许我一直以来缺的就是...橄榄球\NMaybe this is what I've been missing ... football.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.24,0:07:27.63,SU,,0,0,0,,触地得分!\NTouchdown!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.67,0:07:29.77,SU,,0,0,0,,史蒂文...\NSteven...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.54,0:07:36.67,SU,,0,0,0,,我这段时间来 一直都在想你\NI've been, uh, thinking about you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.68,0:07:39.54,SU,,0,0,0,,比以往更想你\Na lot lately ... more than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.55,0:07:41.11,SU,,0,0,0,,是吗?\NIs that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.15,0:07:43.35,SU,,0,0,0,,是啊,我一生以来\NYeah, well, for my whole life,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.39,0:07:45.42,SU,,0,0,0,,听过很多你的故事\NI've been hearing stories about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.46,0:07:47.22,SU,,0,0,0,,关于你是多么美丽动人的故事\NAbout how amazing you were,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.26,0:07:49.82,SU,,0,0,0,,关于你善良有爱心的故事\Nthat you were so kind and loving.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.86,0:07:51.88,SU,,0,0,0,,每次看到你挂在墙上的\NAnd every time I'd see the painting of you
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.89,0:07:54.26,SU,,0,0,0,,那幅画像,我都能被激励到\Nhanging in the temple, I'd be inspired...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.30,0:07:57.36,SU,,0,0,0,,也会想起身上肩负的责任\Nand reminded of how much I had to live up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.40,0:07:59.23,SU,,0,0,0,,我,呃...\NI, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.27,0:08:03.80,SU,,0,0,0,,我甚至想过把头发染成粉的...还不止一次想过\NI've even thought about dyeing my hair pink ... more than once.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.84,0:08:06.84,SU,,0,0,0,,你现在的发色就挺好的\NThere's nothing wrong with your hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.88,0:08:09.14,SU,,0,0,0,,保持原样就很好\NIt's wonderful just the way it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.18,0:08:13.18,SU,,0,0,0,,各种意义上都很好,就像你一样\NWonderful in every way, just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.78,0:08:18.82,SU,,0,0,0,,哇,这还真好\NWow. This is nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.86,0:08:20.89,SU,,0,0,0,,真的...太好了\NIt's ... it's really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.93,0:08:22.95,SU,,0,0,0,,我...我真的早就该\NI ... I should have tried this
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.96,0:08:24.12,SU,,0,0,0,,来这里试试了\Na long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.16,0:08:26.86,SU,,0,0,0,,但是,史蒂文,你意识到了吗?\NBut, Steven, don't you realize?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:29.29,SU,,0,0,0,,我们一直以来其实都在一起\NWe've been together this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.30,0:08:31.76,SU,,0,0,0,,哦\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.80,0:08:34.53,SU,,0,0,0,,是...是...是这样的\NThat's ... that ... that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.57,0:08:36.10,SU,,0,0,0,,哦\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.14,0:08:38.36,SU,,0,0,0,,这是我们第一次在一起\NThis is the first time we've hung out together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.40,0:08:40.87,SU,,0,0,0,,我得留影做纪念\NI got to capture this moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.67,0:08:44.18,SU,,0,0,0,,除了我之外什么都没有啊\NThere's nothing here but me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.22,0:08:47.35,SU,,0,0,0,,我一直都在自言自语吗\NI'm just talking to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.88,0:08:51.45,SU,,0,0,0,,你不是我妈妈\NYou're not my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.49,0:08:52.75,SU,,0,0,0,,我不是?\NI'm not?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.79,0:08:54.35,SU,,0,0,0,,你只是我对你的印象和想象\NThis is how I want you to be,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.39,0:08:56.99,SU,,0,0,0,,我还是没了解真正的你\Nbut I don't know if this is who you really are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.03,0:08:58.69,SU,,0,0,0,,我知道你的很多事\NI've learned things about you,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.73,0:09:00.83,SU,,0,0,0,,那些你藏作秘密的事\Nthings you wanted to keep secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.87,0:09:02.99,SU,,0,0,0,,你把铋斯姆关进了狮子里\NYou locked Bismuth away inside Lion
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.00,0:09:04.78,SU,,0,0,0,,因为她想粉碎别的宝石\Nbecause she wanted to shatter Gems,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.80,0:09:06.83,SU,,0,0,0,,你还从来没有告诉过石榴和珍珠\Nand you never told Garnet or Pearl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.87,0:09:09.13,SU,,0,0,0,,然后你又粉碎了粉钻\NBut then you shattered pink diamond.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.14,0:09:11.34,SU,,0,0,0,,导致现在母星盯上了地球\NNow all of Homeworld has it out for Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.38,0:09:13.44,SU,,0,0,0,,还有我和水晶宝石们!\Nand the Crystal Gems and me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.48,0:09:17.17,SU,,0,0,0,,你把我们都拉进了危机中,然后又自顾自消失了!\NYou put us all in danger, and you just disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.25,0:09:24.02,SU,,0,0,0,,哇 哇\NWhoa. Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.79,0:09:29.65,SU,,0,0,0,,我终于知道真相了\NI finally know the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.66,0:09:31.36,SU,,0,0,0,,我知道你真面目了\NI know what you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.40,0:09:33.06,SU,,0,0,0,,你是个骗子!\NYou're a liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.10,0:09:35.19,SU,,0,0,0,,我以为你从来不想伤害别人的\NI thought you never wanted to hurt anyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.23,0:09:36.99,SU,,0,0,0,,但是你伤害了所有人!\Nbut you hurt everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.00,0:09:39.93,SU,,0,0,0,,你怎么能抛下石榴紫晶和珍珠\NHow could you just leave Garnet and Amethyst and Pearl
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.97,0:09:41.50,SU,,0,0,0,,还有...还有老爸?\Nand ... and Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.54,0:09:43.90,SU,,0,0,0,,她们离了你根本不知所措!\NThey don't know what to do without you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.94,0:09:45.97,SU,,0,0,0,,也许她们根本在你心中\NMaybe they didn't matter to you as much as
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.01,0:09:47.67,SU,,0,0,0,,还没有藏起你那些破事重要!\Nhiding from the mess you made!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.71,0:09:49.91,SU,,0,0,0,,这就是我存在的原因,对吧?\NAnd that's why I'm here, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.95,0:09:51.84,SU,,0,0,0,,你创造了我只是为了\NDid you make me just so you wouldn't have to
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.88,0:09:54.31,SU,,0,0,0,,让我处理你犯下的错误?\Ndeal with all your mistakes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.92,0:10:00.82,SU,,0,0,0,,我存在的目的就是这个吗?\NIs that all I'm here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.86,0:10:03.99,SU,,0,0,0,,史蒂文,你知道根本不是这样的\NSteven, you know that isn't true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.03,0:10:06.39,SU,,0,0,0,,我留给你的录像带里,我告诉过你\NIn the tape I left you, I told you how much
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.43,0:10:09.13,SU,,0,0,0,,我是多想让你存在在这个世界上\NI wanted to have you and let you exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.17,0:10:12.80,SU,,0,0,0,,你觉得我在录像带里说的话都是谎言吗?\NDo you think what I said to you in the tape was a lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.97,0:10:16.10,SU,,0,0,0,,不 我很确定\NNo. I'm sure ...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.14,0:10:18.94,SU,,0,0,0,,我很确定你说的都是真心话\NI'm sure you meant it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.28,0:10:23.64,SU,,0,0,0,,我明白了\NI get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.68,0:10:26.84,SU,,0,0,0,,我知道你不是有意让我处理你的错误\NI know you didn't want me to deal with your problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.85,0:10:28.55,SU,,0,0,0,,但是你现在是我的一部分了\NBut you're a part of me now,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.59,0:10:31.35,SU,,0,0,0,,我现在得对付你留下的那些事了\Nand I have to deal with what you left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.77,0:10:49.67,SU,,0,0,0,,嘿,史嘟宝!\NHey, Shtu-ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.71,0:10:52.37,SU,,0,0,0,,猜猜谁买了牛仔短裤\NGuess who's back in jean shorts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.41,0:10:55.31,SU,,0,0,0,,猜猜谁给你带了披萨\NAnd guess who also got you a pizza.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.35,0:10:58.34,SU,,0,0,0,,-就是我!-老爸!\N- It was me! - Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.38,0:11:00.64,SU,,0,0,0,,紫晶!石榴!\NAmethyst! Garnet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.65,0:11:02.15,SU,,0,0,0,,还有珍珠?\NAnd Pearl, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.19,0:11:04.08,SU,,0,0,0,,辣肠披萨卖完了\NThey were all out of pepperoni, by the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.12,0:11:06.45,SU,,0,0,0,,我只能给你带蘑菇的了\Nso I just got you mushroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.49,0:11:09.67,SU,,0,0,0,,-希望你不介意吧 -简直完美\N- I hope that's all right. - It's perfect.
